Package fr.warzou.virtualcard.api.environment

This package contain every classes used to manage the card environment.

Developers could use EnvironmentComponent for implement bit easier modules with a predefined init methode. See EnvironmentComponent.init(fr.warzou.virtualcard.api.Card)
